text: Noel Keith Miller (1 July 1913 - 26 November 2007) was an Australian cricketer. He played one first-class match for New South Wales in 1935/36. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1913 births Category:2007 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers
